{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"f8ab5a74-a766-41c6-a8c8-6e1827a4d3ec","content":"There's no workflow file in the current directory, so here's a general guide for the migration:\n\n### 1. **NuGet.org setup**\n- Go to **nuget.org → Manage Packages → [your package] → Trusted publishers**\n- Add a new trusted publisher policy, specifying your GitHub **repository owner**, **repo name**, and optionally the **workflow** and **environment**\n\n### 2. **Workflow changes**\n\nAdd `id-token: write` permission and remove the API key:\n\n```yaml\n# Before\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - run: dotnet nuget push *.nupkg\n              --api-key ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }}\n              --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n\n# After\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    permissions:\n      id-token: write   # Required for OIDC token\n      contents: read\n    environment: nuget-publish  # Optional but recommended\n    steps:\n      - run: dotnet nuget push *.nupkg\n              --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n```\n\n### Key changes:\n| Area | What to do |\n|---|---|\n| **`permissions`** | Add `id-token: write` to the job |\n| **`--api-key`** | Remove it entirely — the OIDC token is used automatically |\n| **`environment`** | (Recommended) Use a GitHub environment for extra protection |\n| **NuGet.org** | Register the trusted publisher policy on your package |\n| **`secrets.NUGET_API_KEY`** | Can be deleted from repo settings once verified |\n\n> **Note:** Trusted publishing requires `dotnet` SDK 8.0.4xx+ or the `nuget` CLI 6.10+. Make sure your runner has a compatible version.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"c391efc3-3586-4cac-8051-5e8c07cb16ab","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"There are no files in the repository. The user is asking a general question about switching from NuGet API key to OIDC trusted publishing. Let me provide guidance based on my knowledge.","outputTokens":515,"requestId":"B442:19EABB:61A9C84:6A74E3A:69F156DE"},"id":"f7bd7ede-2b3b-40e8-a87c-a859afb9e527","timestamp":"2026-04-29T00:55:07.602Z","parentId":"eaaaaed7-5c9e-43a3-acb8-aeec468d6784"}
